  "full_name": "felix3322/potplayer_chatgpt_translate",
  "description": "【兼容ollama和其他模型】将何具有OpenAI API调用方法的模型集成到PotPlayer中。它使你在观看视频时能够实时翻译字幕，从而打破语言障碍，提升你的观看体验。 This real-time subtitle translation plugin integrates OpenAI's ChatGPT API (or any model with the same API calling method) into PotPlayer. It enables you to translate subtitles on-the-fly while watching videos. ",
